name:
Photon 1.12 
(c) 2021 ermouth 

Run attachment `index.html` to start Photon. 

See https://github.com/ermouth/couch-photon 
repo for more details.
versions:
## 1.12.2

New feature: Photon is able to dump selected DBs into ZIP archive, and 
to restore from it; accessible as new option in [Sync/dump…] dlg.

Src/tgt inputs of [Sync/dump…] dlg knows about DBs that were created/deleted
when the dlg is open.

Fixed: glitches in filtering `_deleted` docs while sync.

## 1.11.15

The `_design_docs` filter for a DB now shows total data and disk sizes
for all DB indices.

## 1.11.12

Fixed forward `_changes` navigation. Couch performance test is fixed 
and is now accessible from About tab.

## 1.11.10

Added `_node/_local/_nodes` endpoint, visible as a DB in Couch 3+ (#31). 
JSON editor node Takeout/Extend window allows system keys clean up.

## 1.11.5

Fixes `_local/*` docs viewer (#29).

## 1.11.4

Added forward navigation through Changes feed, also fixed minor glitches.

## 1.11.3

Fixed disappearing map functions having comments before fn definition (#28).

Fixed Erlang MapReduce views editor rejecting valid functions.

## 1.11.2

Added Changes feed view, default direction for `/_changes` is reverse. 

Rubberband scroll behavior in Chromium-based browsers is now disabled. 

Login popup no more offers to create ‘safe’ password in Safari. 

Stats monitor shows dates for older series.

## 1.10.12

Fixes missing direction selector for Mango Index views (#27). Added log direction selector
into Log viewer for Couch 1.x.

## 1.10.11

CLI installation script updated to reflect CouchDB 3 tight default security for newly created 
DBs. Confusing behavior of View editor after saving a view under new name is fixed.

## 1.10.10

Reloading default mango index no more switches to All docs view, also blocks saving invalid 
Mango index ddocs in certain circumstances (#26). 

## 1.10.8

Package size reduced, .eot version of icon font is no more included.

## 1.10.7

Viewindex rows are now pretty-printed when expanded. Reload btn now only updates 
selected docs/ddocs if any. Package size reduced – JS and CSS optimized a bit.

## 1.10.4

Fixes ddoc list displayed incorrect index sizes after compaction.

## 1.10.2

List of design docs now shows space occupied by indices. [Compact…] dlg in ddocs list respects 
ddocs selected, if any. Default scroll is now native, not NiceScroll.

## 1.9.40

Small UI improvements.

## 1.9.39

For CouchDB 3.0: added partiotioned DBs support in [New DB] dlg. 

New (i) button in each row of DB list shows popup with raw DB info.


## 1.9.36

For CouchDB 3.0: fixed non-admin login issues, also added non-admin alternative for navigating 
across DBs.

Folding/unfolding speed of `_attachments` branches having hundreds of files is slightly improved.

## 1.9.33

For Couch 2.x+ Photon always uses bulk `/_dbs_info` to get buckets info. Photon is now compatible
with newly released CouchDB 3.0.0.

## 1.9.31

Btn [Clear] removed from the [Copy…] dlg. Btn [New doc] is now [Create user…] when in `_users` DB.
[Delete DBs] dlg now contains node hostname to avoid “wrong tab” errors. [Save config] dlg 
for clusters now shows readable node name in [Save] btn.

## 1.9.30

Each viewindex row now have a chechbox, which selects related doc and all other visible
rows emitted from the doc. Selection survives switching from viewindex to doc list 
and vice versa.

When docs are deleted, they are always re-read right before deletion/purging to ensure 
valid revisions.

## 1.9.25

Fixed invalid documentation links in Config. Fixed resize glitches for [New sync] and 
[New DB] dlgs being dragged.

## 1.9.22

Added `perftest.html`, which is superficial CouchDB perf test.

Fixed: iPadOS Safari is validly detected; 401/403 `_session` debounce interval decreased to 1s; 
no more group task selection glitches for groups having escaped chars; [New Sync] target
login/pwd now works fine in Couch 1.x.

## 1.9.21

Glitches with restoring tabs are fixed now. Also several minor UI fixes.

## 1.9.20

Update repo now can be path to external `_design/photon` doc. Updates are shipped with short description. 

## 1.9.18

Added update reminder and search by user name across couch_persuser-style DBs. 

## 1.9.6

Added DB backup feature, a dialog to create several sync tasks at a turn. Also added groups to task list. 

## 1.8

Improved JSON editor, added `/_stats` graphs.

## 1.7

Added structured diff for doc revisions.

## 1.6

New feature: editor for text-based attachments.

Added doc purge; DB view received `db/_design_docs` and `db/_local_docs` filters.

## 1.4

Added access restrictions, Photon no more starts without authorization.

## 1.2

Added in-place Erlang, JS and Mango view/index editors.

## 0.9.99

More or less usable version with all basic features. March, 2018.
